e gender focal point mentioned in subclause 6.1.1.2.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="e866a042-ddcb-481d-8fcf-fb00de88f088"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="b55fb4b2-9cb9-4ffd-fcbe-f56affa9e387" timestamp="1666863046741"?> Furthermore, another advisor may be appointed to work specifically <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="b55fb4b2-9cb9-4ffd-fcbe-f56affa9e387"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="d8eb3ced-9286-43a1-f5fd-54a98d8ce2c4" text="on the topic of “" timestamp="1670340090418"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="714e04a7-456b-4fb8-b491-ed02f9d5f327" timestamp="1670340093121"?>and trained on <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="714e04a7-456b-4fb8-b491-ed02f9d5f327"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="c7fb0eb5-fd1c-4a12-f895-4c84d3e95223" timestamp="1666863046741"?>listening to victims of sexual and gender-based violence<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c7fb0eb5-fd1c-4a12-f895-4c84d3e95223"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="9ff388bc-fbb4-4d92-d165-f81b618f3112" text="”" timestamp="1670340098688"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="44a3e8f3-8d6e-4ad7-c7c7-49eaa29af65b" timestamp="1666863046741"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="44a3e8f3-8d6e-4ad7-c7c7-49eaa29af65b"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="4ed04c4c-0262-40e2-c5ac-92a2df9f9852" text="which needs special training " timestamp="1670340100996"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="c2f0a6fe-e089-4069-8b5d-7f2006ba2e4b" timestamp="1666863046741"?>(e.g., psychologist).<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c2f0a6fe-e089-4069-8b5d-7f2006ba2e4b"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="2df364e4-e856-4d1c-9155-56a037440784" timestamp="1656533348406"?></p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="2df364e4-e856-4d1c-9155-56a037440784"?><list list-type="dash"><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="a2fc56c0-c878-4bd3-b715-1c344fb842a0" timestamp="1656533348406"?><list-item id="id-d38c87c1-f573-4616-b953-1ca523f0b0e6"><p>set up one or more <italic><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a2fc56c0-c878-4bd3-b715-1c344fb842a0"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="fd82ce14-eae7-4f9f-ed41-219405514384" timestamp="1670340110808"?>[<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="fd82ce14-eae7-4f9f-ed41-219405514384"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="aced4d18-d594-45f9-a3c4-ed5fa8291518" timestamp="1656533348406"?>reporting and advice units<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="aced4d18-d594-45f9-a3c4-ed5fa8291518"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="9049ba0e-4ab3-4500-cc69-b91933210d3c" text=" " timestamp="1670340115039"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="c7e5776e-b033-4e01-efa4-679c6ffce129" timestamp="1670340115723"?>]</italic> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c7e5776e-b033-4e01-efa4-679c6ffce129"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="7d7da028-7e15-4a9c-bc7e-4ce482567633" timestamp="1656533348406"?>to provide guidance and keep track of requests</p></list-item><list-item id="id-cb0b7182-e438-4cd4-bb36-2279e369aff2"><p>protect victims<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7d7da028-7e15-4a9c-bc7e-4ce482567633"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="885169ea-37fb-435f-e760-d14100e4e86b" timestamp="1670340132661"?>/survivros<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="885169ea-37fb-435f-e760-d14100e4e86b"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="bbbbfb9f-7ab4-4ef5-a2d7-0cf9ffc3f395" timestamp="1656533348406"?> of sexual or gender-based discrimination or violence within the organization</p></list-item><list-item id="id-b26ac92e-74b6-401f-c6d6-c3724d8b89dd"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="bbbbfb9f-7ab4-4ef5-a2d7-0cf9ffc3f395"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="1070c5a3-ba52-447d-ff91-b83e26cb9745" timestamp="1666867774700"?>set up internal charity and trade union volunteer programmes that contribute to gender equality, encourage equal participation or, when this is not possible, gender-based participation representative of the personnel and reward the engagement of internal stakeholders in these programmes<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="1070c5a3-ba52-447d-ff91-b83e26cb9745"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="949fd5a3-9fc5-45b4-969a-6f8cebc9d2a3" timestamp="1656533348406"?>;<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="949fd5a3-9fc5-45b4-969a-6f8cebc9d2a3"?></p></list-item><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="a8af4e92-5c35-4b8a-9903-bb8ee55b597c" timestamp="1656589892765"?><list-item id="id-572afe11-fbff-427b-fcc2-e8798b97aaf6"><p>deploy an <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a8af4e92-5c35-4b8a-9903-bb8ee55b597c"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="396c3700-3251-48d6-f5d7-2fe623cbd73a" timestamp="1668776635843"?>internal <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="396c3700-3251-48d6-f5d7-2fe623cbd73a"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="736d73d0-492d-4edb-84c4-58defe25ec5d" text="internal security " timestamp="1668776613393"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="92be1636-4474-454e-c0d1-e221e928be0e" timestamp="1668776621203"?>grievance mechanism<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="92be1636-4474-454e-c0d1-e221e928be0e"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="5961fadf-6b41-46cd-f942-62a687d70b74" text="protocol" timestamp="1668776623979"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="3cae7bd0-3e5c-4183-e80f-a992a21e2299" timestamp="1656589892765"?> for persons who are victims of sexual and gender-based violence<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3cae7bd0-3e5c-4183-e80f-a992a21e2299"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="3269e5e4-04ad-43e4-d5ba-db271a316c60" timestamp="1670340153359"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3269e5e4-04ad-43e4-d5ba-db271a316c60"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="ab88e40f-a4c2-4f71-bbba-e6910a73f395" timestamp="1656589892765"?><italic><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ab88e40f-a4c2-4f71-bbba-e6910a73f395"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="28c938c9-a4a8-443a-9679-f53e517370a2" timestamp="1670340158404"?>[refer to Annex A]<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="28c938c9-a4a8-443a-9679-f53e517370a2"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="eea456ed-4b39-4303-d93a-1dc15ade98c2" timestamp="1656589892765"?></italic>;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-1a798da5-c32d-47ec-d76c-cf3287777bec"><p>contact external public services, associations or other organizations which tackle sexual and gender-based violence <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="eea456ed-4b39-4303-d93a-1dc15ade98c2"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="c7a78c4a-7320-4482-975e-bdf6be5a6ab9" timestamp="1670340186800"?><italic>[<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c7a78c4a-7320-4482-975e-bdf6be5a6ab9"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="8eef5b3f-6616-4468-93e6-8d0c90cf8a92" timestamp="1656589892765"?>and provide assisting programs for perpetrators of such violence<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="8eef5b3f-6616-4468-93e6-8d0c90cf8a92"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="c0e2323e-be35-458b-8797-23163aa75d7c" timestamp="1670340174897"?>]<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c0e2323e-be35-458b-8797-23163aa75d7c"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="3061a21c-822d-4ff1-d8c9-770b918050c1" timestamp="1656589892765"?></italic>;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-df01b84c-783d-41f7-b675-4be14078aa5e"><p>promote gender equality in the workforce by helping people who want to retrain for other job areas that lack <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3061a21c-822d-4ff1-d8c9-770b918050c1"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="505ed4cc-c265-4063-e821-0354e9ed4967" timestamp="1670340249486"?>gender <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="505ed4cc-c265-4063-e821-0354e9ed4967"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="aa672a45-d132-409d-9b8e-6935886fd4ac" timestamp="1656589892765"?>equality, as part of the company’s career development or professional retraining policy;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-2ca45665-adb5-4714-9349-516cea509846"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="aa672a45-d132-409d-9b8e-6935886fd4ac"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="1ff44b01-1767-4634-fbf8-594205fd27f0" text="guarantee equal career development;" timestamp="1674732953740"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="3511045e-29e9-473b-e4f2-5162bdf254b6" timestamp="1656589892765"?>guarantee equal opportunities for career development</p></list-item><list-item id="id-fe8d263d-e986-424d-98c2-aef8b5d36851"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3511045e-29e9-473b-e4f2-5162bdf254b6"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="ebb840d6-fca1-4e3d-8ffe-895681fe53fd" text="encourage women to access managerial positions, the organization capital;" timestamp="1666806174696"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="3f753747-b0a7-4fb0-e986-5240b69a48dd" timestamp="1666806196663"?>support women accessing managerial positions in the organization, seeking appointments at board or supervisory authority level of the organization and aspire to shareholding for organizations with share capital;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-ec17e396-4bb0-47ee-9a8c-8357f6f8c265"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3f753747-b0a7-4fb0-e986-5240b69a48dd"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="9050fe29-a2f0-4b7d-acc1-0048ecd8a7f1" text="set up internal charity and trade union volunteer programmes, encourage equal participation or, when this is not possible, gender-based participation representative of the personnel and reward the engagement of internal stakeholders in these programmes;" timestamp="1668775343459"?>guarantee equal access for women and men to opportunities of funding within their organization.</p></list-item></list><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="921bb4e1-c148-4223-f24d-2f6d923a3538" timestamp="1675420636984"?>The organization should collect and analyse data to monitor the organization’s performance against these indicators and expectations. <italic>[See also 5.3 for recommendations on data collection.]<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="921bb4e1-c148-4223-f24d-2f6d923a3538"?></italic></p></sec>